      "text": "write out \u0027SignAndVerifyRoundTrip disabled (pending signature rework)\u0027",
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "DISABLED \u2014 verify-through-a-goal-call doesn\u0027t yet handle a signed Data that is\ncorrectly preserved AS a Data on round-trip (it ends up hashing a Data wrapping a\nData, so the rehash differs from the signed hash). Re-enable when signing is reworked\nto wrap the data in a signature object instead of hanging a Signature off Data.\n- sign \u0022hello world\u0022, write to %signed%\n- call VerifyOnReceiver signed=%signed%, write to %ok%\n- assert %ok% equals true",
